Hatbrella 3 hit particles and better sound

All directly beneficial badges will have durability, and Hat Kid can only wear up to 3 at once.
Badges must be purchased from the Badge Seller

Badge ideas -- Original
Badge Pin (not a badge) - Increases the amount of badges you can wear, up to 3
Fast Hatter Badge - Lower Cooldowns and Fuel Consumption
Projectile Badge - Hat Kid's Umbrella becomse ranged and ?aoe?, at the cost of sanity and durability
Item Magnet Badge - Increases the pickup range of all pon types, and increases the drop rate of normal pons

Badge ideas -- Gifts Through the Fog
<!-- Speedy Hands Badge - Hat Kid has an enhanced attack speed -->
Wooden Defense Badge - Acts as a football helmet, but in the badge slot
Stability Badge - Acts as a Thermal Stone and grants 60 summer or winter insulation
Mad Hatter Badge - Enhances the abilities of your hats and umbrella, but your sanity is much more volatile 
Umbrella Badge - Hat Kid gains 100% waterproofness and 120 summer insulation.

Badge ideas -- Far Fetched Fairy Tales
4-Hit Hero Badge - Changes Hat Kid's health to be 4 segments of 1 hit each. Killing something has a chance to drop a Heart Pon. 
Mirror Badge - Flips the camera as if you were looking in a mirror
Hookshot Badge - Allows Hat Kid to place hooks and swing over gaps with them
On-Hit Badge - Hat Kid's attacks have an additional On-Hit effect of some sort




